ORIGINAL: A rechargeable battery, storage battery, secondary cell, or accumulator is a type of electrical battery which can be charged, discharged into a load, and recharged many times, as opposed to a disposable or primary battery, which is supplied fully charged and discarded after use.
ENGLISH: A rechargeable battery, storage battery, secondary cell, or accumulator is a type of electrical battery which can be charged, discharged into a load, and recharged many times, as opposed to a disposable or primary battery, which is supplied fully charged and discarded after use.
CZECH: Dobíjecí baterie, akumulátory, sekundární články nebo akumulátory jsou druhy elektrických baterií, které lze nabíjet, vybíjet do zátěže a mnohokrát dobíjet, na rozdíl od jednorázové nebo primární baterie, která je dodávána plně nabitá a vyřazená po použití.
GERMAN: Eine wiederaufladbare Batterie, Akku oder Sekundärzelle ist eine Art einer elektrischen Batterie, welche mehrfach aufgeladen und entladen werden kann, im Gegensatz zu Einwegbatterien, welche nur einmal genutzt werden können.
RUSSIAN: Перезаряжаемая батарея, аккумуляторная батарея, или аккумулятор - это тип электрической батареи, которая может быть заряжена и перезаряжена много раз, в отличие от одноразовой батареи, которая поставляется полностью заряженной и утилизируется после использования.
POLISH: Bateria,lub akumulator, jest typem elektronicznej baterii którą można naładować, rozładować ładunek, oraz naładować wielę razy, w porównaniu do zwykłej baterii, która jest dostarczona w pełni załadowana, i którą się wyrzuca po użytku.
HUNGARIAN: Az újratölthető elem, akkumulátor, másodlagos elem vagy akkumulátor olyan típusú elektromos akkumulátor, amelyet többször is fel lehet tölteni, kisütni és újratölteni, szemben az eldobható vagy elsődleges akkumulátorral, amelyet teljesen feltöltve szállítanak, merülés után eldobható.
ITALIAN: Una batteria ricaricabile, batteria secondaria o accumulatore, è un tipo di batteria elettrica che può essere ricaricata, scaricata e ricaricata più volte, al contrario delle batterie primarie che sono vendute cariche e inutilizzabile una volta esaurite.
SPANISH: Una batería recargable, batería de almacenamiento, celda secundaria o acumulador es un tipo de batería eléctrica que se puede cargar, descargar en una carga y recargar muchas veces, a diferencia de una batería desechable o primaria, que se suministra completamente cargada y desechada después de utilizar.
FRENCH: Une batterie d'accumulateurs, ou plus communément une batterie, est un ensemble d'accumulateurs électriques reliés entre eux de façon à créer un générateur électrique de tension et de capacité désirée. Ces accumulateurs sont parfois appelés éléments de la batterie ou cellules.
CHINESE: 可充電電池，儲能電池，二次電池或蓄電池是一種可以充電，放電到負載，並多次充電的電池，與一次性或主要電池相對，後者在使用後被丟棄。
PORTUGUESE: Uma bateria recarregável, bateria de armazenamento, célula secundária ou acumulador é um tipo de bateria elétrica que pode ser carregada, descarregada em uma carga e recarregada várias vezes, em oposição a uma bateria descartável ou primária, fornecida totalmente carregada e descartada após usar.
JAPANESE: 充電可能なバッテリー。一般的な使い捨て電池などとは異なり、充電器などを利用して繰り返し使用が可能なバッテリーです。
CHINESESIMP: 可充电电池、蓄电池或者二次电池可以多次充电使用。单次电池仅能使用一次。

ORIGINAL: A hose is a flexible hollow tube designed to carry fluids from one location to another.
ENGLISH: A hose is a flexible hollow tube designed to carry fluids from one location to another.
CZECH: Hadice je ohebná dutá trubice určená k přenášení tekutin z jednoho místa na druhé.
GERMAN: Ein Schlauch ist ein flexibles Hohlrohr, mit dem Flüssigkeiten von einem Ort zum anderen transportiert werden können.
RUSSIAN: Рукав высокого давления (РВД) — это гибкий трубопровод для транспортировки специальных гидравлических и моторных жидкостей на базе минерального масла, жидкого топлива, консистентных смазок, гликоля или водной эмульсии под давлением, для передачи рабочего усилия.
POLISH: Wąż to elastyczna pusta rura zaprojektowana do przenoszenia płynów z jednego miejsca do drugiego.
HUNGARIAN: A hose is a flexible hollow tube designed to carry fluids from one location to another.
ITALIAN: Un tubo retato preposto a trasportare fluidi tra due punti di un circuito idraulico.
SPANISH: Una manguera es un tubo vacio diseñado para transportar fluidos entre dos puntos
FRENCH: Un tuyau est un tube creux flexible conçu pour transporter des fluides d'un endroit à un autre.
CHINESE: 軟管是一種柔軟的中空管，設計用於將液體從一個地點運送到另一個地點。
PORTUGUESE: Uma mangueira é um tubo oco flexível projetado para transportar fluidos de um local para outro.
JAPANESE: A hose is a flexible hollow tube designed to carry fluids from one location to another.
CHINESESIMP: 软管是一种柔性空心管，旨在将流体从一个位置输送到另一个位置。

ORIGINAL: The igniter plug of a turbine engine ignition system differs considerably from the spark plug of a reciprocating engine ignition system. Its electrode must be capable of withstanding a current of much higher energy than the electrode of a conventional spark plug.
ENGLISH: The igniter plug of a turbine engine ignition system differs considerably from the spark plug of a reciprocating engine ignition system. Its electrode must be capable of withstanding a current of much higher energy than the electrode of a conventional spark plug.
CZECH: Zapalovací svíčka zažehne jednou v určitém čase v motorovém cyklu, aby zahájila jedinou explozi.
GERMAN: Die Zündkerze eines Turbinenmotors unterscheidet sich maßgeblich von der eines kolbengetriebenen Motors. Ihre Elektrode muss fähig sein, einer viel höheren Stromstärke standzuhalten, als die einer konventionellen Zündung.
RUSSIAN: Свеча зажигания зажигается один раз в определенное время в цикле двигателя, чтобы вызвать взрыв, который двигает поршень.
POLISH: Świeca zapłonowa iskrzy raz na określony czas w cyklu silnika, aby wywołać pojedynczą eksplozję.
HUNGARIAN: The igniter plug of a turbine engine ignition system differs considerably from the spark plug of a reciprocating engine ignition system. Its electrode must be capable of withstanding a current of much higher energy than the electrode of a conventional spark plug.
ITALIAN: Una candela d'accensione. Scocca una scintilla in un tempo specifico durante un ciclo per innescare la combustione
SPANISH: Una bujia crea chispas con un tiempo determinado para poder producir explosiones
FRENCH: Une bougie d'allumage, étincelle une fois à un moment précis du cycle du moteur pour déclencher une seule explosion.
CHINESE: 渦輪引擎點火系統的點火塞與往復式引擎點火系統的火星塞有很大不同。 它的電極必須能夠承受比傳統火星塞電極高得多的能量。
PORTUGUESE: Um plugue de ignição acende uma vez em um momento específico do ciclo do motor para acionar uma única explosão.
JAPANESE: The igniter plug of a turbine engine ignition system differs considerably from the spark plug of a reciprocating engine ignition system. Its electrode must be capable of withstanding a current of much higher energy than the electrode of a conventional spark plug.
CHINESESIMP: 点火塞在发动机循环中的特定时间产生一次火花以引发一次爆炸。

ORIGINAL: The Land Rover Defender, initially introduced as the Land Rover 110, is a series of 4x4 off-road pick-up trucks. The vehicle, a British equivalent of the Second World War derived (Willys) Jeep, gained a worldwide reputation for ruggedness and versatility
ENGLISH: The Land Rover Defender, initially introduced as the Land Rover 110, is a series of 4x4 off-road pick-up trucks. The vehicle, a British equivalent of the Second World War derived (Willys) Jeep, gained a worldwide reputation for ruggedness and versatility

ORIGINAL: The UAZ-469 is an all-terrain, all-purpose military vehicle manufactured by UAZ. It was used by the armed forces of the Soviet Union and other Warsaw Pact countries, as well as paramilitary units of the Eastern Bloc. ... The classic military version offers seven seats.
ENGLISH: The UAZ-469 is an all-terrain, all-purpose military vehicle manufactured by UAZ. It was used by the armed forces of the Soviet Union and other Warsaw Pact countries, as well as paramilitary units of the Eastern Bloc. ... The classic military version offers seven seats.
CZECH: UAZ-469 je terénní vojenské vozidlo vyráběné společností UAZ. Bylo používáno ozbrojenými silami Sovětského svazu a dalších zemí Varšavské smlouvy a také paramilitárními jednotkami Východního bloku. Klasická vojenská verze nabízí sedm sedadel.
GERMAN: The UAZ-469 is an all-terrain, all-purpose military vehicle manufactured by UAZ. It was used by the armed forces of the Soviet Union and other Warsaw Pact countries, as well as paramilitary units of the Eastern Bloc. ... The classic military version offers seven seats.
RUSSIAN: УАЗ-469 - это вездеход, универсальный военный автомобиль производства УАЗ. Его использовали вооруженные силы Советского Союза и других стран Варшавского договора, а также полувоенные формирования Восточного блока. ... Классическая военная версия предлагает семь мест.
POLISH: The UAZ-469 is an all-terrain, all-purpose military vehicle manufactured by UAZ. It was used by the armed forces of the Soviet Union and other Warsaw Pact countries, as well as paramilitary units of the Eastern Bloc. ... The classic military version offers seven seats.
HUNGARIAN: The UAZ-469 is an all-terrain, all-purpose military vehicle manufactured by UAZ. It was used by the armed forces of the Soviet Union and other Warsaw Pact countries, as well as paramilitary units of the Eastern Bloc. ... The classic military version offers seven seats.
ITALIAN: L'UAZ-469 è un veicolo militare per ogni terreno e multiruolo prodotto da UAZ. E' stato usato dalle Forze Armate della ex Unione Sovietica ed altri del Patto di Varsavia, così come da gruppi paramilitari del Blocco Orientale. La classica versione militare è dotata di sette posti.
SPANISH: The UAZ-469 is an all-terrain, all-purpose military vehicle manufactured by UAZ. It was used by the armed forces of the Soviet Union and other Warsaw Pact countries, as well as paramilitary units of the Eastern Bloc. ... The classic military version offers seven seats.
FRENCH: L'UAZ-469 est un véhicule militaire tout-terrains, tout-usages fabriqué par UAZ. Il a été utilisé par les forces armées soviétiques et des autres pays du Pacte de Varsovie, ainsi que par des unités paramilitaires du bloc de l'Est. ... La version classique militaire offre sept places assises.
CHINESE: UAZ-469 是一款由UAZ製造的全地形多用途軍用車輛。它曾被蘇聯和其他華沙條約組織國家的武裝力量以及東方集團的準軍事部隊所使用。... 其經典的軍用版本提供七個座位。
